                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ma foi, vous avez bien raison,\nVous pour qui tout est floraison\nParfumant les pieds de vos lys,\nDe ne pas célébrer Phyllis"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Vous qui pouvez chaque matin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Bercé par le flot de satin",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Voir dans l'or de votre salon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Tomber les flèches d'Apollon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous qui pouvez chaque matin,\nBercé par le flot de satin\nVoir dans l'or de votre salon\nTomber les flèches d'Apollon,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mais pour nous qui, jusqu'à présent,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Soupons sous la treille en causant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "(Et c'est notre meilleur repas !)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ami, ne nous enlevez pas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais pour nous qui, jusqu'à présent,\nSoupons sous la treille en causant\n(Et c'est notre meilleur repas !)\nAmi, ne nous enlevez pas"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Dans les fleurs, près de frais bassins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Nous nous couchons sur des coussins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "La pourpre au dos, vous le savez !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et dans des bains de stuc pavés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans les fleurs, près de frais bassins,\nNous nous couchons sur des coussins\nLa pourpre au dos, vous le savez !\nEt dans des bains de stuc pavés"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Le col paré de nos présents,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "De belles filles de seize ans",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Avec le charme oriental,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Le vin du Rhin dans ton cristal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le col paré de nos présents,\nDe belles filles de seize ans\nAvec le charme oriental,\nLe vin du Rhin dans ton cristal,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "O nuit d'étoiles sous les cieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Jardins, nectar délicieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Nous les possédons en effet,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Mais, hélas ! ce beau monde est fait",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "O nuit d'étoiles sous les cieux !\nJardins, nectar délicieux,\nNous les possédons en effet,\nMais, hélas ! ce beau monde est fait"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Sans elle et ses prismes fleuris,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Pour pouvoir chercher hors Paris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Qui court dans les gazons naissants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Il nous faudrait bien quatre cents",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sans elle et ses prismes fleuris,\nPour pouvoir chercher hors Paris\nQui court dans les gazons naissants,\nIl nous faudrait bien quatre cents"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Ou, je frissonne d'y penser !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Nous n'oserions pas nous passer",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "De perdre un quart d'heure aux genoux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "De Cidalise. Ah ! laissez-nous",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ou, je frissonne d'y penser !\nNous n'oserions pas nous passer\nDe perdre un quart d'heure aux genoux\nDe Cidalise. Ah ! laissez-nous"
        }
